<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>開戶申請已送出｜口袋證券</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --header-h: 80px;
        --page-max: 1440px;
        --bg-page: #f5f5f5;
        --header-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        --title-coral: #e95465;
        --link-blue: #0056c7;
        --text: #3e3a39;
        --muted: rgba(62, 58, 57, 0.65);
        --border: #e8e4e3;
        --footer-start: #c01846;
        --footer-end: #e65967;
        --btn-salmon: #e95465;
      }

      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        font-family: "Noto Sans TC", "PingFang TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg-page);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      body > .site-header {
        width: 100%;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .shell {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        max-width: var(--page-max);
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .site-header {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 30;
        width: 100%;
        height: var(--header-h);
        background: #fff;
        box-shadow: var(--header-shadow);
      }

      .site-header__inner {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 2px minmax(0, 1fr);
        column-gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        max-width: var(--page-max);
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        padding: 0 max(24px, env(safe-area-inset-left)) 0 max(24px, env(safe-area-inset-right));
      }

      .brand-logo {
        grid-column: 1;
        display: block;
        line-height: 0;
      }

      .brand-logo__img {
        height: 46px;
        width: auto;
        max-width: min(240px, 42vw);
        object-fit: contain;
        display: block;
      }

      .brand-divider {
        grid-column: 2;
        width: 2px;
        height: 35px;
        background: var(--title-coral);
        justify-self: center;
      }

      .header-text-cluster {
        grid-column: 3;
        width: 100%;
        min-width: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px 20px;
      }

      .page-title {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--title-coral);
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .license-link {
        color: var(--link-blue);
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
      }

      .license-link:hover {
        opacity: 0.85;
      }

      .site-main {
        flex: 1;
        width: 100%;
        background: var(--bg-page);
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px 24px 56px;
      }

      .success-card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 520px;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 40px 32px 44px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .success-card__title {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--title-coral);
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      .success-card__body {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: var(--text);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .success-card__qr {
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
      }

      .success-card__qr img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: contain;
        display: block;
      }

      .success-card__qr-fallback {
        display: none;
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border: 2px dashed var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: repeating-conic-gradient(#f0f0f0 0% 25%, #fff 0% 50%) 50% / 16px 16px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.4;
        padding: 12px;
      }

      .success-card__qr-fallback.is-visible {
        display: flex;
      }

      .success-card__qr-fallback__hint {
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      .success-card__qr-note {
        margin: -12px 0 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .success-card__line {
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .success-card__line strong {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .btn-home {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 14px 40px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: var(--btn-salmon);
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: opacity 0.15s;
      }

      .btn-home:hover {
        opacity: 0.92;
      }

      .site-footer {
        width: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(78deg, var(--footer-start) 0%, var(--footer-end) 100%);
        padding: 40px 16px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .site-footer__text {
        max-width: 900px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-family: "PingFang TC", "Noto Sans TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        :root {
          --app-header-bar-h: 64px;
          --app-header-stack: 76px;
        }

        .shell {
          max-width: 100%;
        }

        .site-header {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: none;
          height: auto;
          min-height: 0;
          box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(110, 110, 110, 0.1);
        }

        .site-header__inner {
          box-sizing: border-box;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: row;
          flex-wrap: nowrap;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: stretch;
          gap: 14px;
          min-height: var(--app-header-bar-h);
          height: auto;
          max-width: none;
          width: 100%;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 2px max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-left)) 2px max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-right));
          background: #fff;
        }

        .brand-logo {
          display: flex;
          flex: 0 0 auto;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-self: stretch;
          min-width: 0;
          min-height: 0;
          line-height: 0;
        }

        .brand-logo__img {
          display: block;
          width: auto;
          height: 100%;
          max-height: 100%;
          max-width: min(240px, 52vw);
          object-fit: contain;
          object-position: left center;
        }

        .brand-divider {
          flex-shrink: 0;
          width: 3px;
          border-radius: 2px;
          align-self: stretch;
          min-height: 52px;
          margin: 1px 0;
          background: rgba(233, 84, 101, 0.55);
        }

        .header-text-cluster {
          display: flex;
          flex: 1 1 auto;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: flex-start;
          align-self: stretch;
          gap: 3px;
          min-width: 0;
          width: auto;
        }

        .header-text-cluster .license-link {
          display: inline-block;
          max-width: 100%;
          text-align: left;
          white-space: nowrap;
          overflow: hidden;
          text-overflow: ellipsis;
          font-size: clamp(11px, 3.2vw, 15px);
          line-height: 22px;
        }

        .page-title {
          margin: 0;
          color: #f95868;
          font-size: 20px;
          font-weight: 500;
          line-height: 28px;
          letter-spacing: 0.01em;
          white-space: normal;
        }

        .license-link {
          color: #0056c7;
          font-weight: 400;
        }

        .site-main {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: none;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 24px max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-left)) 40px max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-right));
          box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .success-card {
          max-width: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header" role="banner">
      <div class="site-header__inner">
        <a href="index.html" class="brand-logo" aria-label="口袋證券首頁">
          <img
            class="brand-logo__img"
            src="images.png"
            width="220"
            height="46"
            alt="口袋證券"
          />
        </a>
        <span class="brand-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <div class="header-text-cluster">
          <p class="page-title">線上開戶</p>
          <a class="license-link" href="#">金管會證總字第0047號</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="shell">
      <main class="site-main" role="main">
        <div class="success-card">
          <h1 class="success-card__title">您已成功送件申請！</h1>
          <p class="success-card__body">
            口袋證券已收到您的開戶申請文件，審查人員正在檢核中，還請您稍作等待。預計兩小時開戶完成後，將以簡訊及
            Email 通知。
          </p>
          <div class="success-card__qr">
            <img
              id="successQrImg"
              width="200"
              height="200"
              alt="加入官方 Line 之 QR Code（每次載入隨機產生示意）"
            />
            <div id="successQrFallback" class="success-card__qr-fallback" aria-hidden="true">
              QR<br />示意<br /><span class="success-card__qr-fallback__hint">（外部服務無法載入）</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="success-card__qr-note" id="successQrNote"></p>
          <p class="success-card__line">
            立即加入 Line 官方帳號：<strong>@popo6620</strong><br />
            讓您快速掌握最新活動與資訊，感謝您選擇口袋證券！
          </p>
          <a class="btn-home" href="index.html">返回首頁</a>
        </div>
      </main>

      <footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
        <div class="site-footer__text">
          口袋證券股份有限公司｜新北市板橋區三民路一段216號9樓｜客服專線0809-089-001
          08:00~17:00（週一至週五，非交易日除外）<br />
          建議瀏覽器：Edge、Chrome、Safari、Firefox 以上最新版本<br />
          © 口袋證券 版權所有 1.4.1.12
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
    <script>
      (function () {
        var img = document.getElementById("successQrImg");
        var fb = document.getElementById("successQrFallback");
        var note = document.getElementById("successQrNote");
        if (!img) return;

        if (note) note.textContent = "正在產生動態 QR…";

        var rand =
          Date.now().toString(36) +
          "-" +
          Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 10) +
          "-" +
          Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 8);
        var payload =
          "https://line.me/R/ti/p/@popo6620?utm_source=success_demo&ref=" + rand;
        var url =
          "https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=220x220&margin=10&ecc=M&data=" +
          encodeURIComponent(payload);

        img.addEventListener("load", function () {
          if (fb) {
            fb.classList.remove("is-visible");
            fb.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
          }
          if (note)
            note.textContent =
              "以下 QR 為示意：每次重新整理會產生不同圖樣（內容仍為官方 Line 連結格式）。";
        });
        img.addEventListener("error", function () {
          img.style.display = "none";
          if (fb) {
            fb.classList.add("is-visible");
            fb.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false");
          }
          if (note) note.textContent = "無法產生動態 QR，改以版面示意顯示。";
        });

        img.src = url;
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
